      <title>由于对增长和产品策略的质疑，特斯拉预计将降低利润率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-expected-post-lower-profit-margin-amid-doubts-growth-product-strategy-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉预计将在周二公布六年多以来的最低毛利率，此前经历了混乱的一周，包括大规模裁员、汽车降价以及投资者迫切要求明确产品策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-expected-post-lower-profit-margin-amid-doubts-growth-product-strategy-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 19:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
